snippet.title: Asfalia Trailer - March 2023
snippet.description:
Asfalia is beautifully hand drawn point & click video game tale about emotions for children. 

Help Charlie explore Asfalia, the mysterious world of emotions. Meet lovable quirky characters and help them with their problems. 

Solve simple environmental puzzles. Collect stickers, and save Asfalia from an imminent danger.

Discover more on our website: http://asfalia.funtomata.com/
